gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Trail Blazers 103, Cavaliers 95
gameRecap.excerpt: The Trail Blazers defeated the Cavaliers, 103-95, after outscoring them 63-49 in the second half. Shaedon Sharpe led Portland with 29 points, 10 rebounds, and five assists as Jerami Grant (13 points, 3-6 3PT) and Malcolm Brogdon (11 points, seven assists) combined for 24 points. Donovan Mitchell (23 points, seven rebounds, six assists) and Evan Mobley (20 points, eight rebounds) led Cleveland. Portland improves to 5-12 on year as the Cavaliers move to 10-9.
